{"tid":1789194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【拜金黐人夫】傅嘉莉自嘲無腦白痴 深切反省：我也不完美","createTime":"2019-12-19T09:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T19:18:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb46c0c0fdb80053ed03e5d3f1e9292e727d99bd","tid":1789194,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"34歲傅嘉莉入行多年緋聞不絕，曾被影到在的士內啜爆新加坡已婚富豪肥叔叔，前年又與有米人夫莊天龍蜜遊越南，身邊男伴都是有婦之夫的有錢佬，搞到自己形象插水，被冠上拜金第三者之名；昨晚傅嘉莉在社交網有感而發，自嘲無腦白痴，自我反省。<br />\n傅嘉莉寫道：「我常常問自己一個問題，人喜歡聽好話，不喜歡聽壞話，但心卻常常忘記好話，全記掛着所有的壞話而不開心，俗語說，愛一個人，不應該為一棵樹，放棄整個森林，如果這個道理是對的，我們是否不應該介意一個人的惡評，而放棄整個森林的好評？」<br />\n臨近年尾，傅嘉莉表示要自我反省：「沒有人是完美，我也不完美，但也要愛自己，開心正面生活，你們說，對嗎？無腦白痴的傅嘉莉上 #12月的有感而發 #2019年最後2星期 #沒有一個人能滿足全世界 #每天反省一件事」有網民都留言鼓勵：「會反省的人是有腦㗎，仲好有腦嗰隻」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191219/large/1576743837_a340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576743837_a340.jpg&h=42702f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191219/60395647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60395647&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=410c1c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60395647&h=df0f1f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191219/60395647</a>"},{"pid":"effb0d98a58202ef21e18a68f7b9aa6483d65438","tid":1789194,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"想中出"},{"pid":"39912095070fde4f3728c79365bd96f2e5964289","tid":1789194,"uid":65218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"effb0d98a58202ef21e18a68f7b9aa6483d65438","tid":1789194,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"ci